libs.content:
find_library(
      libuv_tmp_library
      names uv libuv
      hints $env{conda_prefix}\\library
      path_suffixes lib
      required
      no_default_path)

find_program(
      glslc_path glslc
      paths
      env vulkan_sdk
      paths "$env{vulkan_sdk}/${cmake_host_system_processor}/bin")

deps.context: find_package(opencv 4 quiet components core highgui imgproc imgcodecs optflow videoio video)
find_package(opencv 3 quiet components core highgui imgproc imgcodecs videoio video)
find_package(opencv quiet components core highgui imgproc)

libs.content:
find_library(openmp_${_openmp_implicit_lib_plain}_library
                names "${_openmp_implicit_lib_name}"
                doc "path to the ${_openmp_implicit_lib_plain} library for openmp"
                hints ${openmp_${lang}_implicit_link_dirs}
                cmake_find_root_path_both
                no_default_path
              )

find_library(benchmark_library
  names benchmark
  no_system_environment_path
  doc "the benchmark library"
)

find_library(gloo_native_library
  names gloo
  doc "the gloo library (without cuda)"
)

find_library(gloo_cuda_library
  names gloo_cuda
  doc "the gloo library (with cuda)"
)

find_library(${_prefix}_${_library}_library
          names ${_library} paths env lib paths env path)

find_library(leveldb_library names leveldb
                             paths /usr/lib $env{leveldb_root}/lib
                             doc "path to leveldb library." )

find_library(${_prefix}_${_library}_library
          names ${_library}
          paths env lib
          paths env path )
find_library(atlas_cblas_library names  ptcblas_r ptcblas cblas_r cblas       paths ${atlas_lib_search_paths})
find_library(atlas_lapack_library names lapack alapack_r alapack lapack_atlas paths ${atlas_lib_search_paths})
find_program(matlab_mex    names mex    mex.bat    hints ${matlab_dir} path_suffixes bin no_default_path)
find_program(matlab_mexext names mexext mexext.bat hints ${matlab_dir} path_suffixes bin no_default_path)

find_program(cuda_toolkit_root_dir_nvcc
    names nvcc nvcc.exe
    paths
      env cuda_toolkit_root
      env cuda_path
      env cuda_bin_path
    path_suffixes bin bin64
    doc "toolkit location."
    no_default_path
    )

find_program(cuda_toolkit_root_dir_nvcc
    names nvcc nvcc.exe
    paths /opt/cuda/bin
    path_suffixes cuda/bin
    doc "toolkit location."
    )

find_library(gflags_library_release
        names libgflags
        paths ${gflags_root_dir}
        path_suffixes release)

find_library(gflags_library_debug
        names libgflags-debug
        paths ${gflags_root_dir}
        path_suffixes debug)
